Comment: 1,0:01:56.92,0:01:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{}
Dialogue: 1,0:02:04.01,0:02:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, here I am.
Dialogue: 1,0:02:08.39,0:02:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:15.90,0:02:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Father?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:17.42,0:02:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:30.16,0:02:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this...
Dialogue: 1,0:02:48.93,0:02:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaho!
Dialogue: 1,0:02:50.76,0:02:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaho! Kaho!
Dialogue: 1,0:02:52.94,0:02:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,My brother! What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:55.36,0:02:57.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You're back from America?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:57.93,0:03:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, my project has slowed down a bit.
Dialogue: 1,0:03:01.32,0:03:04.99,Default,,0,0,0,,But once I arrived, I found my dear\NKaho had moved out on her own...
Dialogue: 1,0:03:05.48,0:03:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,...with father and the rest gone\Nto some random villa or the like.
Dialogue: 1,0:03:09.32,0:03:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The place is utterly deserted!
Dialogue: 1,0:03:12.86,0:03:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And so you got in touch with me.
Dialogue: 1,0:03:16.14,0:03:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,From all your phone messages\Nand telegrams, it seemed serious.
Dialogue: 1,0:03:20.13,0:03:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I got worried and came by.
Dialogue: 1,0:03:22.29,0:03:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It all worked out.
Dialogue: 1,0:03:24.26,0:03:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It brought us siblings\Ntogether again, just the two of us—
Dialogue: 1,0:03:27.10,0:03:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,and for that, I'm glad.
Dialogue: 1,0:03:29.01,0:03:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,But, hey, what's with all these kokeshi dolls?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:34.22,0:03:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes—aren't they all so adorable?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:37.39,0:03:39.45,Default,,0,0,0,,There are lots of theories behind kokeshi...
Dialogue: 1,0:03:39.90,0:03:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,...but I like the one where the\Nname means "child transformed."
Dialogue: 1,0:03:43.81,0:03:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,When I could not cherish you,\NI would make a kokeshi, coo over it,
Dialogue: 1,0:03:48.10,0:03:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,and distract myself from my loneliness.
Dialogue: 1,0:03:50.79,0:03:54.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, but today is the best day ever for me!
Dialogue: 1,0:03:55.57,0:03:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I am grateful, ever so grateful\Nthat you have come, Kaho!
Dialogue: 1,0:04:02.21,0:04:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you leave this place\Nand start living on your own?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:07.84,0:04:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought it over, in my way.
Dialogue: 1,0:04:10.52,0:04:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I... I'm so sad.
Dialogue: 1,0:04:14.11,0:04:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,My darling delicate Kaho,\Nsullied and shattered in the big city...
Dialogue: 1,0:04:19.91,0:04:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It made me realize that I'd grown\Ntoo dependent on you and my family...
Dialogue: 1,0:04:24.75,0:04:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,...as you tried to protect me.
Dialogue: 1,0:04:26.81,0:04:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, depend on me!
Dialogue: 1,0:04:28.92,0:04:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Lean on me {\i1}so hard{\i0}...
Dialogue: 1,0:04:33.04,0:04:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not just that.
Dialogue: 1,0:04:34.95,0:04:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,All my own problems...
Dialogue: 1,0:04:38.05,0:04:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I blamed them on my family, on everyone else.
Dialogue: 1,0:04:41.34,0:04:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 1,0:04:43.50,0:04:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,By all means, go ahead and blame me.
Dialogue: 1,0:04:47.52,0:04:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all my fault. I went to America
Dialogue: 1,0:04:52.12,0:04:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,and couldn't rescue you\Nwhen you were in anguish.
Dialogue: 1,0:04:55.76,0:04:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's not your fault.
Dialogue: 1,0:05:00.85,0:05:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, I've been wondering.
Dialogue: 1,0:05:04.37,0:05:07.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Why exactly did you go to America, anyway?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:07.95,0:05:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother and father said they didn't\Nknow the reasons behind it, either.
Dialogue: 1,0:05:12.84,0:05:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, never mind about me!
Dialogue: 1,0:05:17.50,0:05:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,H-How about we watch some TV? Hmm?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:38.05,0:05:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I know...
Dialogue: 1,0:05:39.50,0:05:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,...tonight we shall dine on beautiful Echizen crab!
Dialogue: 1,0:05:42.79,0:05:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my!
Dialogue: 1,0:05:47.36,0:05:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Crab, crab, crab...
Dialogue: 1,0:05:56.76,0:05:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, where did you get this car?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:59.90,0:06:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a rental.
Dialogue: 1,0:06:01.37,0:06:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You rented it for me?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:04.33,0:06:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess so.
Dialogue: 1,0:06:05.73,0:06:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you so nice to me, anyway?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:11.88,0:06:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I lost my mom, too, when I was about your age.
Dialogue: 1,0:06:17.14,0:06:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Seeing you reminds me of my childhood...
Dialogue: 1,0:06:21.97,0:06:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,And I can't let you be.
Comment: 1,0:06:24.39,0:06:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh.
Dialogue: 1,0:06:25.56,0:06:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,But you sure are mean to Kaho.
Dialogue: 1,0:06:28.79,0:06:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like she's the only one I'm mean to.
Dialogue: 1,0:06:33.86,0:06:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The woman my dad remarried was like that.
Dialogue: 1,0:06:38.02,0:06:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate wishy-washy women.
Dialogue: 1,0:06:40.91,0:06:42.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Wishy-washy?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:42.47,0:06:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,But Kaho...
Dialogue: 1,0:06:55.53,0:06:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Come, you must be hungry.
Dialogue: 1,0:06:57.68,0:06:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Dinner is ready at last.
Dialogue: 1,0:07:00.00,0:07:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I had no time to prepare—
Dialogue: 1,0:07:01.45,0:07:03.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid this meager meal\Nis all the caterer could offer.
Dialogue: 1,0:07:04.41,0:07:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Our household's sensibilities\Nare as wonky as ever.
Dialogue: 1,0:07:07.89,0:07:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just right.
Dialogue: 1,0:07:09.27,0:07:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's dig in.
Dialogue: 1,0:07:11.61,0:07:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{Bon appetit.}Let's dig in.
Dialogue: 1,0:07:17.24,0:07:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That seasoned seaweed\N{\i1}would{\i0} remind me of Kanade...
Dialogue: 1,0:07:22.03,0:07:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What is it?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:24.04,0:07:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Gimme your seaweed.
Dialogue: 1,0:07:25.26,0:07:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, uh, here.
Dialogue: 1,0:07:27.42,0:07:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 1,0:07:29.38,0:07:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Was it not to your liking?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:32.71,0:07:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It was.
Dialogue: 1,0:07:44.48,0:07:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaho sucked on these very crab shells\Nwith her own darling mouth.
Dialogue: 1,0:07:50.18,0:07:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And this is the pit from the picked plum
Dialogue: 1,0:07:53.40,0:07:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,that Kaho placed in\Nher mouth and licked all over!
Dialogue: 1,0:08:00.12,0:08:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother{Daikoku}?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:02.43,0:08:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,How did you find your bath?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:04.55,0:08:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for letting me go first.
Dialogue: 1,0:08:07.02,0:08:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It felt great.
Dialogue: 1,0:08:08.39,0:08:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Good to hear.
Dialogue: 1,0:08:10.32,0:08:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You must be exhausted.
Dialogue: 1,0:08:12.26,0:08:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I used a futon dryer to\Nget your bed nice and fluffy.
Dialogue: 1,0:08:18.13,0:08:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... I'm going back to Tokyo tomorrow.
Dialogue: 1,0:08:22.64,0:08:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,To Tokyo?!
Dialogue: 1,0:08:23.86,0:08:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 1,0:08:24.85,0:08:26.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a little longer?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:27.10,0:08:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You came all this way—why\Nnot take it easy for a while?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:30.85,0:08:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,This just...
Dialogue: 1,0:08:32.28,0:08:34.45,Default,,0,0,0,,...feels like I'm running away.
Dialogue: 1,0:08:34.45,0:08:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Running away? What from?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:36.98,0:08:40.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry—I {\i1}am{\i0} exhausted. I'm turning in.
Dialogue: 1,0:08:41.28,0:08:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Good night.
Dialogue: 1,0:08:45.87,0:08:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Good night, Kaho.
Dialogue: 1,0:08:53.04,0:08:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like I'll have any messages... right?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:00.97,0:09:04.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaho seemed a little off somehow.
Dialogue: 1,0:09:08.10,0:09:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What on earth happened to her in Tokyo?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:23.03,0:09:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,A doting brother such as\Nmyself cannot help but worry.
Dialogue: 1,0:09:29.00,0:09:30.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 1,0:09:30.96,0:09:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Kaho.
Dialogue: 1,0:09:32.98,0:09:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Breakfast is served.
Dialogue: 1,0:09:38.94,0:09:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Starting the day with another feast, I see.
Dialogue: 1,0:09:42.26,0:09:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You seemed a bit unwell yesterday...
Dialogue: 1,0:09:45.40,0:09:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,...so I put in a special order with the caterer
Dialogue: 1,0:09:46.96,0:09:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,for snapping-turtle soup and roast eel on rice.
Dialogue: 1,0:09:49.95,0:09:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:50.76,0:09:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I... seemed unwell?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:54.19,0:09:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes{Correct}.
Dialogue: 1,0:09:55.47,0:09:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You may put on a\Nbrave face, but your brother can tell.
Dialogue: 1,0:10:00.44,0:10:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaho... was it something\Npainful that sent you back here?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:07.74,0:10:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,G-Good morning, Kanade!
Dialogue: 1,0:10:12.08,0:10:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't hide anything from you, huh.
Dialogue: 1,0:10:15.25,0:10:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I {\i1}have{\i0} been looking out\Nfor my darling sister all this time.
Dialogue: 1,0:10:20.76,0:10:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,The truth is...
Dialogue: 1,0:10:23.99,0:10:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I fell in love.
Dialogue: 1,0:10:26.89,0:10:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Love?!
Dialogue: 1,0:10:28.00,0:10:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. My first love.
Dialogue: 1,0:10:30.77,0:10:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,And this rogue is in Tokyo?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:33.81,0:10:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What's his occupation?!\NHis pedigree?!
Dialogue: 1,0:10:36.14,0:10:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,He must be quite the smooth\Ncustomer to win your heart!
Dialogue: 1,0:10:40.49,0:10:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, um, actually, it's over.
Dialogue: 1,0:10:42.78,0:10:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I have been dumped.
Dialogue: 1,0:10:44.92,0:10:47.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Dumped?!
Dialogue: 1,0:10:47.37,0:10:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It can't be!
Dialogue: 1,0:10:48.36,0:10:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,There are villains in this world\Nwho would {\i1}dump{\i0} Kaho?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:58.04,0:11:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaho! Come out and play!
Dialogue: 1,0:11:01.84,0:11:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? That voice...
Dialogue: 1,0:11:04.05,0:11:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that Kanade?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:09.16,0:11:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaho! Come out and play!
Dialogue: 1,0:11:12.70,0:11:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You came to {\i1}play{\i0}?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:14.57,0:11:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,So what should I say?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:16.77,0:11:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaho! Come out and make up!
Dialogue: 1,0:11:24.07,0:11:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaho isn't here right now.
Dialogue: 1,0:11:26.36,0:11:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,When is she coming back?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:27.67,0:11:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,She's {\i1}never{\i0} coming back.
Dialogue: 1,0:11:30.40,0:11:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother{Daikoku}!
Dialogue: 1,0:11:31.28,0:11:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 1,0:11:32.94,0:11:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Kaho is {\i1}too{\i0} here!
Dialogue: 1,0:11:35.12,0:11:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Kanade!
Dialogue: 1,0:11:36.22,0:11:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,And Taga...
Dialogue: 1,0:11:38.75,0:11:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing here, Kanade?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:41.09,0:11:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I came to see you.
Dialogue: 1,0:11:42.71,0:11:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,To tell you how I really feel.
Dialogue: 1,0:11:47.97,0:11:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 1,0:11:49.51,0:11:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You lied.
Dialogue: 1,0:11:51.01,0:11:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And you keep getting in the way.
Dialogue: 1,0:11:53.09,0:11:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I beg your pardon?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:55.55,0:11:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Daikoku, this is—
Dialogue: 1,0:11:58.04,0:11:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Who {\i1}are{\i0} you, anyway?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:59.50,0:12:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are {\i1}you{\i0}?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:01.37,0:12:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Her brother!
Dialogue: 1,0:12:02.61,0:12:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Her ex-boyfriend!
Dialogue: 1,0:12:03.48,0:12:04.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Her ex, eh?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:04.97,0:12:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I have heard about {\i1}you{\i0}!
Dialogue: 1,0:12:06.59,0:12:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The shiftless fiend who dumped Kaho!\
Dialogue: 1,0:12:09.43,0:12:11.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I will not forgive you!
Dialogue: 1,0:12:12.90,0:12:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaho! Let's talk over there, alone.
Dialogue: 1,0:12:16.81,0:12:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let you!
Dialogue: 1,0:12:19.94,0:12:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll go off into the shadows, just you two,
Dialogue: 1,0:12:21.89,0:12:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,and you'll sm-sm-sm-smooch\Nor something, I know it!
Dialogue: 1,0:12:25.00,0:12:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Smooch?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:25.95,0:12:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, we have done that already.
Dialogue: 1,0:12:32.22,0:12:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I won't allow it!
Dialogue: 1,0:12:33.66,0:12:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm her brother, and I say no!
Dialogue: 1,0:12:35.80,0:12:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,We shall have a proper duel!
Dialogue: 1,0:12:38.63,0:12:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,A duel?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:41.48,0:12:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Red Light, Green Light!
Comment: 1,0:12:44.01,0:12:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{}
Dialogue: 1,0:12:44.73,0:12:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Gr—
Dialogue: 1,0:12:45.56,0:12:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Green light... red light!
Dialogue: 1,0:12:51.11,0:12:54.01,Alt,,0,0,0,,Green light...
Dialogue: 1,0:12:52.80,0:12:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,This confrontation of the century,\Nwith Kaho on the line,
Dialogue: 1,0:12:55.18,0:12:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,is "Red Light, Green Light"?!
Dialogue: 1,0:12:56.85,0:12:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Green light...
Dialogue: 1,0:12:58.45,0:13:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,So you say, but you sure\Nare going along with it.
Dialogue: 1,0:13:02.38,0:13:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,And just who in blazes are you?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:04.54,0:13:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Red light!
Dialogue: 1,0:13:06.25,0:13:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Tch, no one's moving...
Dialogue: 1,0:13:09.72,0:13:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Green light...
Dialogue: 1,0:13:12.96,0:13:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother{Daikoku}, that's Taga.
Dialogue: 1,0:13:15.35,0:13:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,We live in the same building.
Dialogue: 1,0:13:17.22,0:13:18.89,Default,,0,0,0,,The same building?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:18.89,0:13:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't fret: I have zero interest in your sister.
Dialogue: 1,0:13:23.53,0:13:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Red light!
Dialogue: 1,0:13:25.52,0:13:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Green light...
Dialogue: 1,0:13:27.62,0:13:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know whether to be relieved\Nor insulted by your rudeness.
Dialogue: 1,0:13:31.59,0:13:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaho is super-cute!
Dialogue: 1,0:13:34.32,0:13:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,...and... red light!
Dialogue: 1,0:13:37.41,0:13:41.17,Alt,,0,0,0,,Green light...
Dialogue: 1,0:13:40.25,0:13:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, why is that ex-boyfriend\Nwearing gym clothes?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:45.03,0:13:46.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it that—that "cosplay" thing?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:47.54,0:13:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Believe it or not, he's in fifth grade.
Dialogue: 1,0:13:49.67,0:13:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Primary school.
Dialogue: 1,0:13:51.26,0:13:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Red light!
Dialogue: 1,0:13:52.41,0:13:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Fifth grade, with that appearance?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:54.75,0:13:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough with your joking around!
Dialogue: 1,0:13:57.27,0:13:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Ask your sister if I'm joking.
Dialogue: 1,0:14:01.89,0:14:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Red light!
Dialogue: 1,0:14:04.02,0:14:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,K-Kaho's first love is in primary school...
Dialogue: 1,0:14:08.65,0:14:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,How could I let such a thing\Nhappen to my beloved Kaho?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:19.22,0:14:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Red light!
Dialogue: 1,0:14:20.25,0:14:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I, Nikaidou Daikoku, have made\Nthe biggest mistake in all my 29 years!
Dialogue: 1,0:14:25.72,0:14:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, out!
Dialogue: 1,0:14:27.31,0:14:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaho's brother moved!
Dialogue: 1,0:14:33.88,0:14:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaho, why were you dating a primary-schooler?!
Dialogue: 1,0:14:38.47,0:14:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have a reason.
Dialogue: 1,0:14:40.70,0:14:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I just came to like him.
Dialogue: 1,0:14:43.23,0:14:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,And you even sm-sm-sm-smooched,\Ntoo, didn't you?!
Dialogue: 1,0:14:47.15,0:14:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,But Kanade's dumped me, so...
Dialogue: 1,0:14:52.36,0:14:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{Huh!}Oh...
Dialogue: 1,0:14:53.65,0:14:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, dummy, why do you\Nthink Kanade came here, then?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:58.82,0:14:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:59.37,0:15:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Red light!
Dialogue: 1,0:15:01.42,0:15:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Why? Um...
Dialogue: 1,0:15:03.12,0:15:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, Kaho moved, too!
Dialogue: 1,0:15:07.29,0:15:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 1,0:15:08.38,0:15:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Atsushi's the only one left.
Dialogue: 1,0:15:11.34,0:15:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Green light...
Dialogue: 1,0:15:15.47,0:15:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, you're cut loose.
Dialogue: 1,0:15:17.84,0:15:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw, rats!
Dialogue: 1,0:15:21.93,0:15:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,So I win.
Dialogue: 1,0:15:25.77,0:15:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Since I'm the winner,\NI'll take this idiot girl here.
Dialogue: 1,0:15:30.56,0:15:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Not so fast!
Dialogue: 1,0:15:31.80,0:15:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You just said you had zero interest in Kaho!
Dialogue: 1,0:15:35.72,0:15:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't, but I'll take my prize.
Dialogue: 1,0:15:39.31,0:15:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if it's a consolation pack of tissues.
Dialogue: 1,0:15:41.85,0:15:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Tissues?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:43.62,0:15:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't!
Dialogue: 1,0:15:46.21,0:15:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:47.75,0:15:49.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Refusing to admit you have lost?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:49.64,0:15:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't that go against what\Nyour mother told you, Kanade?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:53.92,0:15:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh—bring up his mother, and Kanade will...
Dialogue: 1,0:15:59.34,0:16:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It does, but...
Dialogue: 1,0:16:01.43,0:16:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,But...?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:04.22,0:16:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,But I still can't hand\NKaho over to you, Atsushi.
Dialogue: 1,0:16:10.40,0:16:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I get it now.
Dialogue: 1,0:16:13.19,0:16:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,My world without Kaho...
Dialogue: 1,0:16:15.98,0:16:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,...was like a hell ruled by\Nthe Dreadlock Lord of Darkness!
Dialogue: 1,0:16:20.45,0:16:22.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooh, Kanade, so close.
Dialogue: 1,0:16:22.19,0:16:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't need that "-lock" in there!
Dialogue: 1,0:16:26.04,0:16:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to see you, talk to you, every day.
Dialogue: 1,0:16:30.29,0:16:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you, Kaho!
Dialogue: 1,0:16:33.29,0:16:34.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Kanade!
Dialogue: 1,0:16:34.49,0:16:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Rich words coming from\Nsomeone who used Kaho so!
Dialogue: 1,0:16:43.10,0:16:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Boy, are you easy.
Dialogue: 1,0:16:45.03,0:16:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Dumped. Depressed. And a single\N"I love you" gets you all moony.
Dialogue: 1,0:16:48.90,0:16:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Cheap as breadcrusts sold for a dime.
Dialogue: 1,0:16:52.69,0:16:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,And yet you get so full of yourself\Nwhen the ducks at the park swarm you.
Dialogue: 1,0:16:57.24,0:17:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I'm itching to make you\Nsee that you're nothing but breadcrumbs.
Dialogue: 1,0:17:00.71,0:17:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,How rude!
Dialogue: 1,0:17:01.71,0:17:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,If Kaho were bread,\Nshe would be a top-shelf baguette!
Dialogue: 1,0:17:05.10,0:17:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,No, a fried bun!
Dialogue: 1,0:17:08.37,0:17:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Either way, what, she's still bread?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:10.03,0:17:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Pardon me?!
Dialogue: 1,0:17:11.42,0:17:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Your attitude is the very definition
Dialogue: 1,0:17:12.81,0:17:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,of how one teases the girl he loves!
Dialogue: 1,0:17:15.75,0:17:18.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps you {\i1}do{\i0} care for Kaho after all!
Dialogue: 1,0:17:18.05,0:17:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it true, Atsushi?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:19.96,0:17:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that why you came with me?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:23.84,0:17:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 1,0:17:25.41,0:17:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I hadn't realized it, but maybe I do.
Dialogue: 1,0:17:29.93,0:17:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I bully her because I love her.
Dialogue: 1,0:17:33.23,0:17:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I love this stupid, simple, wishy-washy,
Dialogue: 1,0:17:36.30,0:17:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,moldy breadcrumb of a girl,\Nnot even fit to feed ducks.
Dialogue: 1,0:17:41.28,0:17:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not something\Nyou say to the girl you love.
Dialogue: 1,0:17:45.35,0:17:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Taga's found a whole new game, that's all.
Dialogue: 1,0:17:50.45,0:17:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to hear what Kaho has to say.
Dialogue: 1,0:17:53.05,0:17:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you!
Dialogue: 1,0:17:54.46,0:17:57.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to go out with me again.
Dialogue: 1,0:17:58.34,0:17:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaho!
Dialogue: 1,0:17:59.67,0:18:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be taken in by his sweet-talking!
Dialogue: 1,0:18:01.55,0:18:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I... can't go back to the way we were, Kanade.
Dialogue: 1,0:18:05.42,0:18:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You're {\i1}not{\i0} being taken in?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:09.06,0:18:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother{Daikoku}...
Dialogue: 1,0:18:10.68,0:18:12.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to speak with Kanade alone.
Dialogue: 1,0:18:16.66,0:18:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The thing is, I do love you, Kanade.
Dialogue: 1,0:18:22.44,0:18:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 1,0:18:23.54,0:18:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm a kid, and too selfish?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:27.53,0:18:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,The way it stands now, we'll just\Nkeep repeating the same old things.
Dialogue: 1,0:18:31.87,0:18:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to be hurt...
Dialogue: 1,0:18:34.80,0:18:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,...and I think I'll start doubting your feelings.
Dialogue: 1,0:18:37.92,0:18:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'll turn into a grown-up you can trust!
Dialogue: 1,0:18:42.92,0:18:48.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I like you the way you are now.\NNo need to grow up in any hurry.
Dialogue: 1,0:18:49.64,0:18:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What I love is you just as you are.
Dialogue: 1,0:18:54.34,0:18:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Then what should I do?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:57.23,0:18:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you remember?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:00.11,0:19:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The day I met you?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:05.61,0:19:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Falling in love with you made me realize:
Dialogue: 1,0:19:09.41,0:19:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew I couldn't stay the same...
Dialogue: 1,0:19:12.49,0:19:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,...that I would have to change.
Dialogue: 1,0:19:16.21,0:19:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't get it at all!
Dialogue: 1,0:19:18.63,0:19:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,If you like me the way I am,\NI like {\i1}you{\i0} the way {\i1}you{\i0} are!
Dialogue: 1,0:19:22.50,0:19:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's stay together.
Dialogue: 1,0:19:25.01,0:19:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Our combo moves will give a huge boost\Nto our power {\i1}and{\i0} our special attacks!
Dialogue: 1,0:19:29.14,0:19:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What is he talking about?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:32.68,0:19:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw it at the school arts\Nfestival in third grade:
Dialogue: 1,0:19:35.48,0:19:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,the prince and princess,\Nbound together for eternity.
Dialogue: 1,0:19:41.15,0:19:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,So: You fell in love with me,\Na primary-schooler. What now?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:46.86,0:19:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,My heart's pounding so fast,\Nand I love Kanade so much...
Dialogue: 1,0:19:51.83,0:19:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care what anyone says.
Dialogue: 1,0:19:54.54,0:19:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to be with him!
Dialogue: 1,0:19:57.25,0:19:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, listen to this:
Dialogue: 1,0:19:59.95,0:20:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,To Kaho, at 15:
Dialogue: 1,0:20:01.91,0:20:03.73,Default,,0,0,0,,"Love Song to Kaho."
Dialogue: 1,0:20:06.36,0:20:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,568)}What is this?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:08.47,0:20:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,568)}It's not excitement...
Dialogue: 1,0:21:19.12,0:21:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaho, let's get married!
Comment: 1,0:23:05.06,0:23:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{}
Dialogue: 1,0:23:35.26,0:23:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Renren here!
Dialogue: 1,0:23:36.60,0:23:38.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Coming up on First Love Monster...
Dialogue: 1,0:23:41.76,0:23:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,All on the next First Love Monster:
Dialogue: 1,0:23:44.10,0:23:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,"A Proper Rom-Com For Once"!
Dialogue: 1,0:23:46.96,0:23:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,And now for a match!
Dialogue: 1,0:23:48.03,0:23:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Renren, chon!
