Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.00,0:20:12.80,song,,0,0,0,,Your love alone is like
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.80,0:20:15.56,song,,0,0,0,,110-million times the power
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.56,0:20:18.53,song,,0,0,0,,No one can steal it away
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.53,0:20:21.36,song,,0,0,0,,Not even the ogres of hell
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.36,0:20:24.25,song,,0,0,0,,It's not that I got hurt
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.25,0:20:27.00,song,,0,0,0,,I hurt you—now
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.00,0:20:32.35,song,,0,0,0,,And then tumbled into hell
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.80,0:20:35.58,song,,0,0,0,,Kaho! Woo!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.58,0:20:38.44,song,,0,0,0,,It's not subtraction, no
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.44,0:20:41.27,song,,0,0,0,,Me! Woo!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.27,0:20:44.11,song,,0,0,0,,It's addition—no, more like
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.11,0:20:46.99,song,,0,0,0,,Multiplication, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.99,0:20:49.89,song,,0,0,0,,Your warmth
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.89,0:20:52.73,song,,0,0,0,,Your upper arms
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.73,0:20:54.21,song,,0,0,0,,Your skin
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.21,0:20:58.05,song,,0,0,0,,Skin, fin, fif—fifteen!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.52,0:21:04.15,song,,0,0,0,,Now all you have to do is nod
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.15,0:21:09.33,song,,0,0,0,,My ticket out of hell—get you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.79,0:21:13.33,song,,0,0,0,,So say "yeah" and get a smooch!
